OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRising prices see regular  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay drop at fastest rate in
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fa decade                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Regular pay is falling at the fastest  
OL,6, rate in more than a decade when taking 
OL,7, into account rising prices, the Office 
OL,8, for National Statistics has said.      
OL,10,FBetween February and April, pay        
OL,11,Fexcluding bonuses was down 2.2% from a 
OL,12,Fyear earlier when adjusted for         
OL,13,Finflation, the ONS said.               
OL,15,FUK household budgets are being squeezed
OL,16,Fby record fuel and energy costs.       
OL,18,FHowever, pay including bonuses is      
OL,19,Foutpacing price rises, rising by 0.4%  
OL,20,Fwhen taking inflation into account.    
